# Server environment variables for PQC LTPA testing
# 
# IMPORTANT: To run PQC LTPA tests, you must configure this server to use Java 26+
# 
# Option 1: Set JAVA_26_HOME environment variable before running tests
#   The test framework will automatically configure the server to use Java 26
#
# Option 2: Manually set JAVA_HOME here (uncomment and update path):
#   JAVA_HOME=/path/to/jdk-26
#
# Without Java 26+, tests will be skipped and server will fall back to LTPA v2 (RSA-only)